    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor but i just need help with the math. my sensitivity factor is usually around 1:50 (meaning 1 unit drops me about 50 points). if i'm at 185 and want to reach 100, how many units should that be? just tell me the calculation so i can handle it.",
